- **PDF**: `{PLATFORM_ROOT}/resume-tailor/tailors/{tailor-id}/Resume_{RoleSlug}_{CompanySlug}_{Date}[_designId].pdf` (derived by export-pdf.mjs when no output path is passed; `_designId` omitted for `ats` only)
